title.rendered: Do Any Apps Interfere With Dumpster?

content.rendered:
Please note that certain apps may interfere with Dumpster’s abilities to save your files. These include task killers, battery savers, and junk file cleaners. We recommend you exclude Dumpster from any similar app’s settings, just in case:

  • Clean Master
  • DU Battery Saver
  • AVG Cleaner
  • Battery Doctor
  • CCleaner
